msgid ""
"You can also use the ``CURRENT_RENDERER`` and ``RENDERER_COMPATIBILITY`` "
"built-in defines for a shader that will work in all renderers:"
msgstr ""
"También puedes usar las definiciones integradas ``CURRENT_RENDERER`` y "
